      "description": "Transform your iPhone's look and feel with Top Widgets⁺. Easily add aesthetic and functional widgets to your Home Screen and Lock Screen. Browse thousands of pre-designed widgets or unleash your creativity with our easy-to-use widget customizer. Plus, discover an endless collection of icon packs, themes, and wallpapers to perfectly match your style and interests. From personalized widgets to custom app icons and wallpapers, Top Widgets⁺ is your ultimate destination for device customization.\n\nUNLIMITED WIDGETS\n\n* Photo Widgets\n* Time, Date & Battery Widgets\n* Countdown Widgets\n* Weather Widgets\n* Control Center Widgets\n* Calendar Widgets\n* Activity Tracking & Pedometer Widgets\n* Clock Widgets\n...and many more!\n\nTHEMES & WALLPAPERS\nDive into the largest collection of themes and wallpapers. With thousands of user-crafted designs that seamlessly blend widgets, icon packs, and wallpapers, you can achieve stunning aesthetics in just a few taps. New themes are added daily by a global community of users and artists, ensuring endless possibilities for personalization.\n\nAESTHETIC ICON PACKS\nRefresh your app icons with our extensive selection of custom icon packs. Replace default icons with designs that match your chosen theme or personal style. Apply icon packs effortlessly with Top Widgets⁺' quick setup, or save them to your camera roll to use with Shortcuts.\n\nMake your iPhone truly yours. Download Top Widgets⁺ now and start customizing your Home Screen and Lock Screen today!\n\nPrivacy Statement\n\n【HealthKit】- TopWidgets⁺ has integrated with HealthKit to synchronize health data into the app. When you record daily step data in TopWidgets⁺, we will request HealthKit data permission to display exercise data in step-related widgets.\n【Location Information】- When using the weather widget, we need to obtain location permission to display the required information for the current widget.\n【Photo Permission】- When adding a background image to a widget, we need to obtain photo permission to upload the background image. This permission is also required when saving images to your phone.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://app.topwidgets.com/agreements/en/privacy.html\nUser Agreement: https://app.topwidgets.com/agreements/en/UserAgreement.html",
